institution: Human Resources Development Service of Korea
category: Internal human resource development support project operation rules/Article 9 (Submission of project implementation result report)
contents: Article 9 (Submission of project implementation result report) When an annual project is completed, the following documents must be attached to the annual implementation result report for each project and submitted to the Minister of Employment and Labor within one month from the date of project completion for the relevant year. , 1. Project budget settlement statement, 2. Evaluation of project implementation contents and effects, 3. Other matters deemed necessary by the Minister of Employment and Labor
